OL,3,CTwo charged over shooting of 15-year-
OL,4,Cold boy in Cardiff
OL,6,FTwo people have been charged in
OL,7,Frelation to the shooting of a 15-year-
OL,8,Fold boy in Cardiff on Saturday 7 June.
OL,10,FThe boy, whose injuries were not life-
OL,11,Fthreatening, was shot on Clos Y
OL,12,FFfynnon in Pontprennau at around 8pm.
OL,14,FAshley Corbin, 20, from Bristol, and a
OL,15,F17-year-old male, also from Bristol,
OL,16,Fwho cannot be named legally because of
OL,17,Fhis age, will appear at Cardiff
OL,18,FMagistrates' Court on Thursday 19 June.
