OL,6,FThey have been charged with two
OL,7,Foffences, conspiring with others to
OL,8,Fhave a firearm, namely a shotgun, with
OL,9,Fintent to commit grievous bodily harm
OL,10,Fand conspiring with others to cause
OL,11,Fgrievous bodily harm with intent.
OL,13,FDetective Superintendent Mark O'Shea,
OL,14,Ffrom South Wales Police, said: "This
OL,15,Fhas and continues to be a complex
OL,16,Finvestigation led by the Major Crime
OL,17,FInvestigation Team of South Wales
OL,18,FPolice.
