OL,6,F"We have deployed all available
OL,7,Fdetectives into this case, to ensure a
OL,8,Frobust policing response, reflective
OL,9,Fof our determination to relentlessly
OL,10,Fpursue anyone who chooses to bring
OL,11,Ffirearms into our communities.
OL,13,F"During the investigation, we have
OL,14,Fbeen working closely with Avon and
OL,15,FSomerset Police which has resulted in
OL,16,Fseveral arrests.
OL,18,F"Now that two people have been
OL,19,Fcharged, we can also confirm that four
OL,20,Fother people have been arrested in
OL,21,Fconnection with the incident.
