OL,6,F"Due to sensitive operational reasons,
OL,7,Fwe have been unable to provide this
OL,8,Finformation publicly until now.
OL,10,F"I would like to thank the community
OL,11,Fof Cardiff for their continued
OL,12,Funderstanding and for the support
OL,13,Fprovided to our detectives.
OL,15,F"Valuable information from the
OL,16,Fcommunity has contributed to the
OL,17,Fsignificant progress we have made
OL,18,Fsince this incident has happened.
