OL,11,Fwith the incident are on police bail
OL,12,Fpending further enquiries into
OL,13,Funrelated matters.
OL,15,FThey are an 18-year-old woman and a 22-
OL,16,Fyear-old man from Newport, as well as
OL,17,Fan 18-year-old man from Cardiff.
OL,19,FA 22-year-old man from Bristol has
OL,20,Fbeen bailed in relation to the
OL,21,Fshooting.
